      <title>日本央行的鷹派低語被日圓的劇烈拋售所淹沒</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japans-hawkish-whispers-drowned-out-by-rowdy-yen-selloff-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上週決定維持政策不變，給日元空頭提供了大量拋售線索，但在蜂擁而至的恐慌中，人們普遍忽視了央行可能在未來幾年分階段加息的信號，並可能在秋季加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japans-hawkish-whispers-drowned-out-by-rowdy-yen-selloff-2024-05-01/</guid>
